HEADWORD: Fellowless
<hw>Fel"low*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without fellow or equal;
peerless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whose well-built walls are rare and <qex>fellowless</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chapman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fellowlike</ent>⟦br⟧
